				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-16/poem-BNgl-5l_4eNXIeLJyIXT-g">Cảm ngộ kỳ 16 - 感遇其十六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/D%E1%BB%B1-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-sxXr_tmnRrcu5DXMsTbxUw">Dự Nhượng kiều - 豫讓橋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-thu%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-g8HuX4x0zTiXCOIOaJzNfQ">Hạ nhật thuật cảm - 夏日述感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-RNpImmo2Zi_8n8IJeKR5eg">Thẩm Đức Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ho%E1%BA%A1-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BA%A1o-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-li%C3%AAn-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-k1biZq1U_QzmFuGmq7CWEQ">Hoạ công bộ Vũ Hạo Trạch vịnh liên nguyên vận kỳ 3 - 和工部武灝澤詠蓮元韻其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/L%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-siSxd_LRjKLCQVHCz0xxvw">Lạc Dương trường cú kỳ 1 - 洛陽長句其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/Ngh%C4%A9a-m%C3%A3-tr%E1%BB%A7ng/poem-cDvZ6PnF-ydowd1CXlWnnQ">Nghĩa mã trủng - 義馬冢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/author-5VBdkDLCcLTpFT7k3ZzmYg">Ngải Tính Phu</a